race.comment: FAST BLUE (5) comes here deep into the campaign and looks to find a weaker contest. Chipped away late with a respectable fifth over 1250m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Stalks the tempo and gets his chance today. KING SOLEIL (3) improving gelding who will appreciate the longer journey. Resumed with an eye catching fourth over 1000m at this track. Comes to hand quickly and gets his chance. MARS LANDING (7) kept fresh and back in trip after fading late when fifth over 1500m at Port Macquarie. Drawn out and look for him late. DARTBROOK (10) improver out to this trip after chipping away late from the wide draw with a battling ninth over 900m at Muswellbrook in C1 company. Can sneak into the minor money from the low draw.
